ist.healthcheck.beans

Class GeneralConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • ist.healthcheck.beans.GeneralConfiguration

  • public class GeneralConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object
    this class contains general information about Database server IP, Database server port Number, ICON database name, SpeechMiner database name, GIM database name, option to enable mail sender, option to enable SMS sender, database username, database password and account name.

    Mohammed Samir
